<p>Due to COVID19 restrictions, the second workshop was delivered as an online video tutorial. The outline can be found in the relevant <a href="https://github.com/krisztian-hofstadter-tedor/web00-website-making-tutorials">GitHub repository</a> and the videos on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRr9g36OjY6-xnDwUx4itRlh-xrlsszNZ">YouTube</a>.</p>

